dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NRock_Roads_2018.gdbN. [This feature class contains all of the roads in Rock County, Wisconsin. They are captured as needed using GPS. The main purpose of this data is for use by 9-1-1 Communications as input into the Computer Aided Dispatch system. They do, however, fit many other purposes as used by other county departments.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
